```csharp
using Pulumi;
using AzureNative = Pulumi.AzureNative;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var connector = new AzureNative.CostManagement.Connector("connector", new AzureNative.CostManagement.ConnectorArgs
        {
            ConnectorName = "AWSBillingAccount",
            CredentialsKey = "arn:aws:iam::123456789012:role/AzureCostManagementRole",
            CredentialsSecret = "external-id",
            DisplayName = "AWS-Consolidated-1",
            Location = "westus",
            ReportId = "HourlyWithResources",
            ResourceGroupName = "rg1",
            Status = "active",
        });
    }

}
```

## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:costmanagement:Connector AWSBillingAccount /subscriptions/01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef/resourceGroups/rg1/providers/Microsoft.CostManagement/connectors/AWSBillingAccount 
```
